  <brief_title>Surveillance of Treatment of Children With Growth Hormone Deficiency With Zomacton®</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-interventional, Observational Study of the Application of Zomacton® in the Treatment of Growth Hormone Deficiency in Routine Clinical Practice</official_title>
