  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the long-term treatment with Zomacton® for
      pituitary short stature in children with insufficient growth hormone production and/or short
      stature caused by Turner's syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
